# Sorting Arrays

## Using Arrays.sort()

```java
import java.util.Arrays;

int[] arr = {5,2,8,1,9};

Arrays.sort(arr);

for(int num : arr)
{
    System.out.print(num + " ");
}
```

Output:

```text
1 2 5 8 9
```

